@ex<EM><EN>The following sequence of Mish-nayos and the selection from Sifra “Rabbi
Yishmael Says,” were inserted after the Scriptural selections dealing with daily-
offerings in order to give every Jew the opportunity to study/ recite daily, the
minimum of selections from Scripture, Mishnah, and Talmud. Even though Sifra is
not actually a Talmudic tractate, it is a Tanaitic expansion of Mishnah. (See
Shulchan Aruch, Orach Chaim 50:1).
